This paper deals with image processing and neural style transfer, which are primarily covered in the computer vision (cs.CV) and graphics (cs.GR) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper discusses the use of neural networks, which falls under the artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-category. The paper also deals with the optimization of the stylization process, which is covered in the machine learning (cs.LG) sub-category. Finally, the paper deals with the processing of large amounts of image data, which is covered in the multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category.
